Title: Trend T32 T32 M Class Dry Vacuum 800W 240V TRET32
Description:
The Trend T32 M Class Dry Vacuum in the 240V version.

The Trend T32 M Class Dry Vacuum is rated to EN 60335-2-69 for dust with workplace limit values > 0.1 mg/m3. With a HEPA H13 filter system and an integrated shaker button for filter cleaning.

It has a large, durable steel tank with a 20 litre capacity. The low flow indicator alerts the user that the suction is dropping and the filter needs to be cleaned. Fitted with a long 5 metre power cable and onboard storage for the power tool adaptor and crevice tool.

Professional Certified: Meets standard 2006/42/EC.

Supplied with:

1 x HEPA H13 Cartridge Filter.
1 x Micro Filter Bag.
1 x Hose 3m x Ø39mm.
1 x Crevice Tool/Brush.
1 x Upholstery Tool.
1 x Power Tool Adaptor - Taper 32-36mm.
1 x High Efficiency Floor Brush.
1 x Hard Floor Brush.
2 x Metal Tube.
1 x Curved Metal Tube.

Specifications:

Input Power: 800W.
Flow Rate: 20 L/sec.
Max. Suction: 146 mbar.
Capacity: Tank 20L, Bag: 15L.
Cable: 5m.
Weight: 6.8kg.
